{"tid":1591920,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"SM計劃明年推出新男團和新女團","createTime":"2019-09-24T11:12:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-26T00:28:09.000Z","uid":213300,"like":1,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"736b154310fd99a46095dfcd5da19f45df3b6610","tid":1591920,"uid":213300,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-24T11:12:03.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/taCNnS2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FtaCNnS2.jpg&h=f5c2c1c4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6EwKp6n.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6EwKp6n.jpg&h=6db0e1fb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nSM總社長金英敏接受採訪表示：<br />\n&gt;&gt;EXO和東方神起將在今年下半年發新專輯。<br />\n&gt;&gt;明年（2020年）會推出新的男團和女團。<br />\n<br />\n&gt;&gt;關於餐飲，觀光，旅遊，文化事業的盈利，最晚到明年年末為止，如果還無法達到目標<br />\n數值且無法改善的話，無論如何都會進行整理，不排除賣掉的可能。<br />\n&gt;&gt; 今年公司的計劃都集中在下半年，專輯銷量上半年為140萬張，僅7丶8月份就超過了這<br />\n數字，如果下半年EXO及東方神起的正規專發行的話，全年銷售額的增長沒有問題<br />\n<br />\n原文：<a href=\"https://www.hankyung.com/finance/article/2019092413661\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hankyung.com%2Ffinance%2Farticle%2F2019092413661&d=CxVPqDM3fecqSGKEY7rAqD4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=e66df59e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hankyung.com/finance/article/2019092413661</a><br />\n<br />\n翻譯：漂亮虎咚咚<br />\n新女團<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1daa7795f6aac745